ComicInfo.Title: Wildstorm Rising Chapter 7
ComicInfo.Summary: Wildstorm Rising Chapter 7: Grifter and Deathblow look up their old Team 7 buddy, Dane, looking for the second key to an ancient Daemonite spaceship. Wetworks heads out to find the key but discovers the WildC.A.T.S waiting for them at their destination. While the two teams duke it out, Hightower finds the key grasped in the hand of the deceased Helspont but, before he can pry it from his cold, dead fingers, Helspont returns to life and takes off with the key.
